data.description: Contemporary 3 bedroom Cudahy ranch home is ready for it's next owner. Spacious main level with living room and family room, eat-in kitchen with appliances included, updated full bath, + 1/2 bath. Lower level with bar ready for rec room finishing touches, laundry room with washer/dryer included, and sump pump. Patio doors to concrete patio, concrete driveway to 2 car attached garage, 1 year home warranty for peace of mind. Don't miss out, call today!
